author: Alex Young
title: Frank Ocean premieres new song “Chanel” — listen
text: Frank Ocean returned to Beats 1 Radio airwaves on Friday night, and he brought along a brand new sonbg. “Chanel” marks the R&B crooner’s first new music since last year’s double helping of Blonde and Endless . You can stream it now via TIDAL , or purchase it via iTunes .
